title: PROJECT ASSESSMENT
content:
Ord. No. 20190822-117, Pts. 39, 40, effective September 1, 2019, repealed the former ยง 30-1-73, and enacted
a new ยง 30-1-73 as set out herein. The former ยง 30-1-73 pertained to disapproval and
denial and derived from City Code Section 25-1-63; Ord. 031211-11; Ord. 031211-42.

An approval of a preliminary plan, final plat, or subdivision construction plan transfers
with the ownership of the land.

Source: City Code Section 25-1-64; Ord. 031211-11; Ord. 031211-42.
